{{Infobox television | | show_name = ''[[Forbes]]'' on Fox | image = forbesonfox.png | caption = | runtime = 30 minutes | creator = | starring = [[David Asman]] | country = United States | network = [[Fox News Channel]] | first_aired = 2002 | last_aired = January 13, 2018 | num_episodes = Unknown }} '''''Forbes on Fox''''' is an American [[business]] analysis program, the third show of the ''[[The Cost Of Freedom|Cost of Freedom]]'' business block, on Saturdays at 11:00&nbsp;a.m. ET on the [[Fox News Channel]]. The show is hosted by [[David Asman]].
''Forbes on Fox'' is the only one of the ''Cost of Freedom'' shows that does not feature any of the "rotating" guest analysts of the block; the show exclusively features the editorial staff of ''[[Forbes]]'' magazine.
In December 2017, it was announced that the ''Cost of Freedom'' block will be replaced by a new two-hour show, ''[[Cavuto Live]]'', hosted by [[Neil Cavuto]], beginning on January 20, 2018.<ref>{{cite press release|title=Fox News Channel Taps Neil Cavuto to Anchor Live Two-Hour Saturday News Program|url=http://press.foxnews.com/2017/12/fox-news-channel-taps-neil-cavuto-to-anchor-live-two-hour-saturday-news-program/|agency=[[Fox News Channel]]|date=December 13, 2017|accessdate=January 19, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/12/neil-cavuto-anchor-saturday-morning-two-hours-fox-news-channel-1202226128/ |last=de Moraes |first=Lisa |title=Neil Cavuto To Anchor Two Hour ‘Cavuto Live’ On Fox News Channel’s Saturdays |date=December 13, 2017 |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]}}</ref>
==Segments== *'''In Focus:''' In the introduction of the program, the first segment covers politics and global events impacting your wallet. This also includes debate about the subject by the panelists. *'''The FlipSide:''' An alternative point of view on a subject, debated upon by the other panelists in the segment. *'''The Informer:''' A segment in which a chosen few of the panelists choose stocks which the others debate whether they are worth a buy or should be avoided at all means.
